channel.title: Is SwiftUI a compatible language with CarLoop OBD-II device
channel.description: I am just curious if I can code using the SwiftUI language and have everything still work as intended with the OBD-II communication device? I'm currently in school and want to do my final project on over the air vehicle diagnostic and communication. Does anyone know if this is something that I'm able to do and if so, do you have any tips for me getting into it?
